dcterms:description: ChemProt is a BioCreative VI dataset consisting of PubMed abstracts for which all mentions of chemical compounds/drugs and genes/proteins are annotated, as well as all intra-sentence relations between the two entity types belonging to a set of relation types of interest.
dcterms:title: ChemProt
